Encode a write call as an estimateGas command for the JS port.

   estimateGas myWriteCall
   -- sends { tag: "estimateGas", contract: ..., method: ..., args: ..., value: ... }
   -- JS responds with { tag: "gasEstimate", gas: "21000" }

